V. Stiviano’s part in the firestorm over Donald Sterling has taken a fresh turn – after she reportedly crashed the Ferrari he gave her.

Miss Stiviano sparked controversy after an audio recording was leaked of the 81-year-old LA Clippers owner launching a racist rant in which he berated his girlfriend for being seen in public with black friends, including Magic Johnson.

Now it has emerged that the 31-year-old has been involved in a road crash, having rolled the Ferrari Mr Sterling is said to have given her as a gift into the back of another car.

