TMZ reports that she was driving the luxury red car behind a Range Rover when she is believed to have failed to stop and rear ended the vehicle in Beverley Hills.

The Range Rover driver has told the website that she was wearing her distinctive visor at the time of the crash.

The report says Miss Stiviano then jumped out of her Ferrari before ‘screaming every obscenity in the book’ telling the driver: ‘You know who you’re messing with, mother f*****?’

When it came to exchanging insurance details by the side of the road, she reportedly refused and asked ‘an assistant’ to do it instead.

